 Trainor|Trainor]]\n! style=\"width:05%;\"| [[Tom Jones (singer)|Jones]] \n! style=\"width:05%;\"| [[Olly Murs|Murs]]\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | 1\n| will.i.am\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;text-align:center;\" | Baby Sol\n| style=\"background:#b0e0e6;text-align:center;\" | So Diva\n| \"[[My Lovin' (You're Never Gonna Get It)]]\"\n| rowspan=7 {{n/a|Team full}}\n| rowspan=7 {{n/a|Team full}}\n| style=\"background:#b0e0e6;|'''{{green|\u2714}}'''\n| rowspan=7 {{n/a|Team full}}\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | 2\n| Meghan Trainor\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;text-align:center;\" | Darci Wilders\n| style=\"background:pink;text-align:center;\" | Katie & Aoife\n| \"[[I Want It That Way]]\"\n| rowspan=6 {{n/a|Team full}}\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | 3\n| Sir Tom Jones\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;text-align:center;\" | ShezAr\n| style=\"background:pink;text-align:center;\" | Lara George\n| \"[[Young Hearts Run Free]]\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | 4\n| Olly Murs\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;text-align:center;\" | Cameo Williams\n| style=\"background:pink;text-align:center;\" | Brian Corbett\n| \"[[Eternal Flame (song)|Eternal Flame]]\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | 5\n| Olly Murs\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;text-align:center;\" | Cat Cavelli\n| style=\"background:pink;text-align:center;\" | Belle Noir\n| \"[[Dance Monkey]]\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | 6\n| will.i.am\n| style=\"background:#fdfc8f;text-align:center;\" | Gevanni Hutton\n| style=\"background:pink;text-align:center;\" | Shauna Byrne\n| \"[[Imagine (John Lennon song)|Imagine]]\"\n|-\n|}\n\n==Knockouts==\n\n===Episode 1 (14 March)===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center; width:65%;\"\n|-\n! Order\n! Coach\n! Artist\n! Song\n! Result\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| Sir Tom Jones\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | So Diva\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[End of Time (song)|End of Time]]\"\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 2\n| Jonny Brooks \n| \"[[Don't Let Me Down (Beatles song)|Don't Let Me Down]]\"\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n! 3\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Zion\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Pray (Sam Smith song)|Pray]]\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| Olly Murs\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Cat Cavelli\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Careless Whisper]]\"\n|-\n! 2\n| Jordan Phillips\n| \"[[Tom Walker (singer)|Rapture]]\"\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n! 3\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Cameo Williams\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Wicked Game]]\"\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| will.i.am\n| Gevanni Hutton\n| \"[[People Help the People]]\"\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n! 2\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Claudillea Holloway\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Paint It Black]]\"\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 3\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Baby Sol\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Blackbird (Beatles song)|Blackbird]]\"\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| Meghan Trainor\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Blaize China\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Light It Up (Major Lazer song)|Light It Up]]\" \n|-\n! 2\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Darci Wilders\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Angel (Sarah McLachlan song)|Angel]]\"\n|-\n! 3\n| Trinity-Leigh Cooper\n| \"[[You Say]]\"\n| style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n|}\n\n===Episode 2 (21 March)===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center; width:65%;\"\n|-\n! Order\n! Coach\n! Artist\n! Song\n! Result\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| Sir Tom Jones\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | ShezAr\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[With a Little Help from My Friends]]\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 2\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Elly O'Keeffe\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Halo (Beyonc\u00e9 song)|Halo]]\"\n|-\n! 3\n| Lois Moodie\n| \"[[Battlefield (song)|Battlefield]]\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| Meghan Trainor\n| Brooke Scullion\n| \"[[Stay (Rihanna song)|Stay]]\"\n|-\n! 2\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Beryl McCormack\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Because You Loved Me]]\"\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 3\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Oli Ross\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Hurt (Christina Aguilera song)|Hurt]]\"\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| Olly Murs\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Alan Chan\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Crazy Horses]]\" \n|-\n! 2\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Ty Lewis\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[I'm So Tired...]]\" \n|-\n! 3\n| Blessing Chitapa\n| \"[[Arlissa|We Won't Move]]\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background:lightgreen;\" | Advanced\n|-\n! 1\n| rowspan=3| will.i.am\n| Lucy Calcines\n| \"[[Attention (Charlie Puth song)|Attention]]\"\n|-\n! 2\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Johannes Pietsch\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[The Winner Takes It All]]\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background:pink;\" | Eliminated\n|-\n! 3\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | Doug Sure\n| style=\"background:pink;\" | \"[[Lost & Found (Jorja Smith album)|Don't Watch Me Cry]]\"\n|-\n|}\n\n==Live shows==\n\n===Results summary===\n;Result's colour key\n:{{Color box|lightgreen|border=darkgray}} Artist received the most public votes\n:{{Color box|pink|border=darkgray}} Artist received the fewest votes and was eliminated\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:85%\"\n|+ Weekly results per artist\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:15%;\"| Contestant\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:20%;\"| Week 1\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:20%;\"| Week 2\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:17%;\"| Round 1\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:17%;\"| Round 2\n|-\n!scope=\"col\" | Blessing Chitapa\n| \n|\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"col\" | Brooke Scullion\n| \n|\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"col\" | Gevanni Hutton\n| \n| \n| \n|-\n!scope=\"col\" | Jonny Brooks\n| 